articles.title: Asian Athletics Championships 2023: Tajinderpal Singh Toor, Parul Chaudhary win gold medals - Olympics
articles.description: Indian shot putter Tajinderpal Singh Toor and steeplechaser Parul Chaudhary won gold medals at Asian Athletics Championships 2023 in Bangkok on Friday. Get results.
articles.content:
Indian shot putter Tajinderpal Singh Toor and runner Parul Chaudhary won gold medals at the Asian Athletics Championships 2023 in Bangkok, Thailand on Friday.
